            <author>Henry Cavendish</author>
            <title level="a" type="main">Essay of a Theory of Electricity</title>
            <date when="1771">1771</date>
            <note>Seems to refer to Cavendish’s “Thoughts Concerning Electricity”, in which he outlines his new theory based on an expansive electric fluid with a greater complexity of forces. He published this theory in the Philosophical Transactions in 1771.</note>
